<HEADER>
A3355 &Cx1f; tad-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FEATURES-BJT08-COX     07-07 0475
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-FEATURES-BJT08-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COX NEWS SERVICE WEDNESDAY FEATURES BUDGET
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   These feature stories for release Wednesday, July 8, 1998, are
