round-trip tickets for just $1 more than the price of first-class,
one-way tickets on the Thalys high-speed train between Paris and
Brussels and other Belgian cities. Tickets must be purchased
between now and Aug. 30 for travel between July 16 and Aug. 30. For
information, call Rail Europe at 888-382-7245.
</P>
