a delightful inn overlooking the ocean. The package includes two
nights' lodging, breakfasts, a lobster dinner, a lobster boat
cruise, or a photo of sensational Nubble Lighthouse for $160 a
person. For information on this classic Maine inn package, call
800-343-3869.
</P>
