<P>
   BORDER-KILLING _ Gunman has killed two Border Patrol agents and
is holed up in a house outside Harlingen. Developing. (Harmon,
Austin American-Statesman).
</P>
<P>
   Eds: Sidebars on victims, gunman possible.
