<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    This SportsNet Plus/Cityline budget for Wednesday, July 8, 1998,
is for audiotex subscribers only. Codes are listed with the UNIX
code first, followed by the QNIX code. All times are Eastern.
