   VISA-SPEEDUP (Washington) -- Plan to boost the number of skilled
foreign workers admitted to the United States stalls in Congress.
Negotating sessions so far have done little to help. By Aaron
Zitner. 700 words.
</P>
<P>
   BANKBOSTON-LAYOFFS (Boston) -- BankBoston to lay off 114
employees in the first stage of a company-wide overhaul designed to
streamline operations. By Lynnley Browning. 500 words.
</P>
