<P>
   Alliant Techsystems Inc., Hopkins, Minn., an aerospace and
military company, received a contract valued at about $1 billion
from Boeing Co. to supply the aircraft maker with composite
structures for the body portion of its Delta 4 family of rockets.
</P>
<P>
