<HEADLINE>
AGENTS OFFER NEW FORUM FOR COMPLAINTS ABOUT AIRLINES 
</HEADLINE>
  (DUPLICATION WARNING: Also moved in `f' news file.) 
(jw) 
 By JANET PIORKO    
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
