<HEADLINE>
MOSHOOD K.O. ABIOLA: FROM WEALTH TO TROUBLED POLITICS TO FLAWED
SYMBOL 
</HEADLINE>
  (With NIGERIA-ABIOLA. Also moving in `i' news file.) 
(bl) 
 By MICHAEL T. KAUFMAN    
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   Moshood Kashimawoo Olawale Abiola, who died Tuesday at the age
