</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GOUGING-TRIAL-1STLD-TEX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
(EDS: FIXES HED) 
TEEN ENTERS PLEA IN EYE GOUGING, IS SENTENCED TO MILITARY SCHOOL
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By MEDE NIX 
c.1998 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
