<DOCNO> NYT19980707.0451 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-07 23:39 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4776 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NY-CHILD-SEX-ABUSE-NY     07-07 0383
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-NY-CHILD-SEX-ABUSE-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
5 INDICTED IN SEX ABUSE OF 3 CHILDREN IN NEW YORK 
</HEADLINE>
   (bl)  
 By MONTE WILLIAMS   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK _ In a case that has raised questions about the city's
monitoring of abused and neglected children under its watch,
prosecutors in Brooklyn handed down a multiple-count indictment
Tuesday charging five adults with a variety of sex offenses
involving three minors.
</P>
<P>
   ``The victims in this case are children who were violated
sexually in a reign of terror,'' Brooklyn District Attorney Charles
Hynes said in announcing the indictments. ``These charges are
deeply disturbing, because the innocence of children is precious.
These defendants are accused of attacking children who had a right
to be loved and cherished.''
</P>
<P>
   The children _ an 8-year-old boy and two girls, sisters ages 13
and 14 _ were raped and sodomized during a five-year span between
1993 and last month, prosecutors said.
</P>
<P>
   Those named in the indictment were Ezra Fremgen, 25, Vincent
Fremgen, 28, both of 149 Starr St., Brooklyn, and Daniel Robacker,
40, Theresa Fremgen, 35, and Curtis James, 35, all of 232 Linden
St., Brooklyn.
</P>
<P>
   Robacker and Ms. Fremgen are the parents of the girls. James is
the father of the boy. And Ezra and Vincent Fremgen are Ms.
Fremgen's brothers.
</P>
<P>
   Among other charges, Ezra Fremgen is accused of forcing his
nieces to engage in oral sex with each other and forcing them to
have oral sex with a dog. Ezra Fremgen is also accused of
videotaping James engaging in sodomy with his son.
</P>
<P>
   Vincent Fremgen is charged with incest in the rape, sodomy and
sexual abuse of his nieces, and Robacker is charged with incest in
the rape, sodomy and sexual abuse of his daughters.
</P>
<P>
   Ms. Fremgen is accused of videotaping her brother, Ezra,
sexually abusing James' 8-year-old son, and James is accused of
raping and sodomizing both girls, sexually abusing his son and
directing him to have sex with a dog while being videotaped.
</P>
<P>
   The most serious charges, rape and sodomy in the first degree,
carry a maximum prison term of 12{ years to 25 years.
</P>
<P>
   ``If these defendants are convicted,'' Hynes said, ``I will ask
for maximum consecutive sentences so that they will never again be
free to threaten or harm another child.''
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
